text: Kim Heung-soo (born 4 October 1980) is a South Korean ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 1998 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of South Korea Category:Ski jumpers at the 1998 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
